    { "risk": "Local key cache invalidation failure — customer revokes CMK but cached DEKs continue to decrypt data", "severity": "critical", "mitigation": "Cannot be fully mitigated without resolving the CMK vs offline contradiction; best effort: short TTL + push invalidation channel" },
