    "recommended_approach": "",
    "files_to_create_or_modify": [],
    "patterns_to_follow": "Envelope encryption is the one pattern that is clearly correct regardless of how contradictions are resolved — use a two-tier key hierarchy (CMK wraps DEK, DEK encrypts data). This enables zero-downtime rotation and decouples key management from data encryption.",
